# Graceful degradation — Redis stopped mid-demo, /predict stays up.
Output screencast/segment6-resilience.mp4
Output screencast/segment6-resilience.gif

Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1500
Set Height 680
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 50ms
Set Padding 18
Set Framerate 12

Hide
Type "clear" Enter
Show

Type "# What happens when the feature store dies mid-request?" Enter
Sleep 1500ms
Type "bash scripts/demo_resilience.sh" Enter
Sleep 20s
